  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You feel an inexplicable power call to you, find the source.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616890/extras/6c46acb372f42d176abd573ca2af33a1.poster.avif?t=1750735186\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616890/extras/6c46acb372f42d176abd573ca2af33a1.webm?t=1750735186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616890/extras/6c46acb372f42d176abd573ca2af33a1.mp4?t=1750735186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each run is different from the last, featuring <strong>random-gen</strong> levels, <strong>artifacts</strong>, and <strong>pseudo-random</strong> weapons. Play through four biomes, fight relentless enemies and bosses who strategically fight to <strong>destroy you</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So don't forget to<strong> burn, slow, knife, bleed, freeze, laser, </strong>and<strong> explode </strong>enemies, <i>to get the upper hand.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Synergize-</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616890/extras/fa88e16ea4057b4bb39c9e9b96065eee.poster.avif?t=1750735186\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616890/extras/fa88e16ea4057b4bb39c9e9b96065eee.webm?t=1750735186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616890/extras/fa88e16ea4057b4bb39c9e9b96065eee.mp4?t=1750735186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Artifacts</strong> are <i>stackable</i> items that give you permanent bonuses for your run. Collect them by opening chests, killing bosses, spending coins, <i>and</i> your own health. Finding <i>synergies</i> between artifacts, character abilities, and weapons, is necessary to win. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Arm Yourself-</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616890/extras/97738046ace242ebd18900c54281f48a.poster.avif?t=1750735186\" width=600 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616890/extras/97738046ace242ebd18900c54281f48a.webm?t=1750735186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616890/extras/97738046ace242ebd18900c54281f48a.mp4?t=1750735186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapon stats <strong>vary</strong> based on rarity. <strong>Higher</strong> <strong>rarities</strong> can result in more extreme variations.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Polished gameplay with responsive controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quick runs, strategic decisions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Memorable bosses, enemies, and<strong> </strong>elite enemy modifiers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >46 artifacts with powerful effects and potential drawbacks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >26 weapons with countless combinations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Partial controller support <i>(I currently recommend mouse & keyboard)</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optional auto-aim (default key: TAB) for accessibility</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You feel an inexplicable power call to you, find the source.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616890/extras/6c46acb372f42d176abd573ca2af33a1.poster.avif?t=1750735186\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616890/extras/6c46acb372f42d176abd573ca2af33a1.webm?t=1750735186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616890/extras/6c46acb372f42d176abd573ca2af33a1.mp4?t=1750735186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each run is different from the last, featuring <strong>random-gen</strong> levels, <strong>artifacts</strong>, and <strong>pseudo-random</strong> weapons. Play through four biomes, fight relentless enemies and bosses who strategically fight to <strong>destroy you</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So don't forget to<strong> burn, slow, knife, bleed, freeze, laser, </strong>and<strong> explode </strong>enemies, <i>to get the upper hand.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Synergize-</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616890/extras/fa88e16ea4057b4bb39c9e9b96065eee.poster.avif?t=1750735186\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616890/extras/fa88e16ea4057b4bb39c9e9b96065eee.webm?t=1750735186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616890/extras/fa88e16ea4057b4bb39c9e9b96065eee.mp4?t=1750735186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Artifacts</strong> are <i>stackable</i> items that give you permanent bonuses for your run. Collect them by opening chests, killing bosses, spending coins, <i>and</i> your own health. Finding <i>synergies</i> between artifacts, character abilities, and weapons, is necessary to win. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Arm Yourself-</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616890/extras/97738046ace242ebd18900c54281f48a.poster.avif?t=1750735186\" width=600 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616890/extras/97738046ace242ebd18900c54281f48a.webm?t=1750735186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616890/extras/97738046ace242ebd18900c54281f48a.mp4?t=1750735186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapon stats <strong>vary</strong> based on rarity. <strong>Higher</strong> <strong>rarities</strong> can result in more extreme variations.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Polished gameplay with responsive controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quick runs, strategic decisions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Memorable bosses, enemies, and<strong> </strong>elite enemy modifiers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >46 artifacts with powerful effects and potential drawbacks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >26 weapons with countless combinations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Partial controller support <i>(I currently recommend mouse & keyboard)</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optional auto-aim (default key: TAB) for accessibility</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
